n one is mistakened. God is not like us human beings, who may show favoritis=\r\nm towards those who praise them or bribe them. The He-aspect of God is a wi=\r\ntness to the play of actions and fruits. The She-aspect of God is the power=\r\n that impartially and impassionately manages the fine balance and order wit=\r\nhin this play of actions and fruits. All beings are equal in Her eyes, from=\r\n the lowest of evil persons to the noblest of saints. She administers just =\r\nand balanced delivery of fruits to actions using\n available agents.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;d=\r\niv&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;The karmas we committed in the past are already in the p=\r\nipeline and will give their results sooner or later. The best we can do wit=\r\nh them, with some effort, is to perhaps reorder them somewhat. The most imp=\r\nortant thing is to not add more serious bad karmas to the pipeline &lt;span st=\r\nyle=3D&quot;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;n&lt;span&gt;ow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; Simply pu=\r\nt, selfish actions and actions that cause pain or harm to others are bad ka=\r\nrmas and selfless actions and actions that cause pleasure or benefit to oth=\r\ners are good karmas.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;When it comes to manipulating the pre-exi=\r\nsting pipeline of karmas awaiting karmaphala, through conscious effort and =\r\ncurrent action, yes, it is possible and general guidelines are available in=\r\n shastras, but we can&#39;t be certain about the specific impact of each action=\r\n. One thing is for sure - remedial measure for overcoming a karma has to be=\r\n commensurate with the karma\n itself.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;You need only small forc=\r\ne to push a cat out of your way, but need a large force to push an elephant=\r\n.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, hel=\r\nvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;=\r\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&g